										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Crypto exchange leader Binance has officially </span><a style="font-size: 16px;" href="https://www.binance.com/en/support/announcement/detail/e719094bd91844a39a5ea5866a1bd19d" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">launched</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a new trading campaign for Zest Protocol (ZEST). The Binance Alpha ZEST Trading competition gives traders the chance to compete for a share of $200,000 in rewards through Binance Alpha.</span></p>
